docs/backlog.md
pd-state.diff.md

# Test-run pollution: workspace-mapping migration writer creates nested
# .claude/pd/migrations/ marker files under plugins/ when suites run from
# package dirs (QA gate 121, pre-existing feature-108 writer — backlog #066).
# Deliberately NOT the root .claude/ (real config lives there).
plugins/**/.claude/
